<c74object name='av.pix.sort' category='' module=''>

    <digest>
        Very basic pixel sorting
    </digest>

    <description>
        A very basic pixel sorting between cell and neighbouring pixel based on hue (color) value. Works well in a feedback loop with av.pix.feedback. The sorting should happen iteratively over a feedback loop to have a proper effect, but it is a quite naive sorting.<br/><br/>

Note: Max 9 users can have a look at jit.fx.pixelsorting and jit.fx.ge.lineinterp for similar effects.

    </description>
    
